node.text: Bump update! 20 wks in a couple days! Every woman looks different during their pregnancy depending on factors such as their height, abdominal muscles, and where the baby is sitting. I’m obviously still very tiny @ 20 wks which is half way through my pregnancy! The baby is actually measuring bigger than most babies! The ultrasound tech’s have told me Milo has giant feet and long legs 😅 so we will be skipping new born clothes when he gets here!
